message.body: All is well in Philly. :) Love my place, my roommates, and what I'm soon to be doing. I'm already inspired and fell in love with life again. Love love love
Oh my darling I am so happy to hear that the feelings are good and that you're in love with life. I wish I could have been there for tonight but I will be there
Soon enough. Sending lots of love and excitement to my philly girl. Enjoy your first full day in the city and settling in
